Test fixture for Lottie file layout similar to dotLottie extract layout:
  animations/<file>.json   — main animation
  images/<file>            — bitmap assets

Asset entries use "u": "/images/..." (leading slash = package root), which must
resolve to this directory (sibling of animations/), not to the filesystem root.

PNG and JSON are minimal data authored for ThorVG unit tests; same license as
ThorVG (MIT).
